{"article_id":"r339nJy5CjqFQadp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"California 's Democratic Attorney General Xavier Becerra said Sunday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he will `` definitely and imminently '' file a lawsuit against the Trump administration","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to contest the declaration of a national emergency at the southern border .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"President Donald Trump declared the emergency on Friday","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"after signing a funding bill","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that included less than a quarter of the money","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"he had requested","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"for the construction of a border barrier ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"he says","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"is necessary","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to stop illegal immigration .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"But Democrats like Becerra do not believe","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"conditions at the border constitute an emergency .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"`` It ' s clear that this isn ' t an emergency","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"- it ' s clear that in the mind of Donald Trump he needs to do something","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to try to fulfill a campaign promise , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Becerra said in an interview on ABC 's `` This Week . ''","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The construction of a border wall has been a central issue for Trump","depth":3},{"id":19,"text":"since he first announced","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"he was running for president in 2015 .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"Previously :","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"Trump declares national emergency","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"to free up billions of dollars for border wall","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"'Dangerous precedent ' :","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"U.S. Chamber joins conservative critics of Trump 's emergency declaration","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"`` That doesn ' t constitute a national emergency","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that would require us to essentially stand down on all sorts of federal laws","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and also violate the U.S. Constitution , ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"said Becerra , a former congressman .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"On Friday , Trump said","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"the emergency declaration and a border wall was needed","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"to combat what he characterized as an `` invasion '' of migrants across the southern border .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"open areas on the border allowed the free flow of drugs and dangerous criminals into the U.S .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"By declaring a national emergency , along with other measures and the $ 1.375 billion","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Congress did approve ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Trump will have about $ 8 billion","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to spend on border barrier construction","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"- far more than the $ 5.7 billion","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he initially demanded .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"White House adviser Stephen Miller ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who is considered one of the chief architects of Trump 's immigration policies ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"pushed back at the idea","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that the president 's action was unconstitutional in an interview Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"`` Congress in 1976 passed the National Emergency Act","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"and gave the president the authority ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"as a result of that ,","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"to invoke a national emergency in many different circumstances , but among them the use of military construction funds , ''","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Miller said on `` Fox News Sunday . ''","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Host Chris Wallace pressed Miller to cite another example from the 59 times","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"presidents used the National Emergency Act","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"where it was invoked","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"to obtain money","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that Congress had refused to appropriate .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Miller did not cite such a precedent","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and took issue with the premise of the question .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` They didn ' t refuse to appropriate it , ''","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Miller said .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"`` They passed a law","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"specifically saying","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"the president could have this authority .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"It ' s in the plain statute .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"That ' s the decision","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that Congress made ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"if people don ' t like that ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"they can address it . ''","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Opponents of Trump 's wall point to government statistics","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that the number of migrants","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"crossing the border annually","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"has declined in recent years .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Many of the migrants","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"who are making the journey","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"are asylum seekers","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"who seek out immigration officials","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"when they arrive at the border .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"They also point to government data","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that show","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that immigrants commit crimes at a lower frequency than U.S. citizens","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and that a wall is unnecessary","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"because most of the drugs and people enter the U.S. at established points of entry .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"On Friday , Trump said","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"he did not find that data credible .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Critics","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"who say","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"the president is using his emergency powers","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"to skirt Congress ' constitutional authority over spending","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"have pointed to his own word","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"when he announced","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"he would declare the emergency .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"`` I didn ' t need to do this .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"But I ' d rather do it much faster , ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Trump said at one point during the lengthy news conference on the White House lawn Friday .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"`` It ' s become clear that this is not an emergency ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"not only because no one believes","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"it is ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"but because Donald Trump himself has said","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"it ' s not , ''","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"Becerra said .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"`` Typically , our presidents have focused on issues","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"where the national interests are clearly at stake .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"The national interests aren ' t at stake here . ''","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"At least two lawsuits already have been filed in response to Trump 's emergency declaration .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"The liberal watchdog group Public Citizen filed a federal lawsuit Friday in Washington , D.C. , just hours after Trump 's announcement .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"The group argues","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Trump exceeded his authority","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and disregarded the separation of powers","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"outlined by the Constitution .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"The suit includes three Texas landowners","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"whose property would be seized by the government through eminent domain","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"to build part of the border barrier .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"A second lawsuit was filed by the watchdog group Citizens for Responsibility and Ethics .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"It argues","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that the White House did not provide the supporting documents","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"needed to justify the national emergency declaration .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Congressional Democrats vowed to do what they can","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"to stop Trump from using his executive authority","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"to shift the Defense Department money toward wall construction .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"`` The Congress will defend our constitutional authorities in the Congress , in the courts , and in the public ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"using every remedy available , ''","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , and Senate Minority Charles Schumer , D-N.Y. , said in a joint statement Friday .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Rep. Joaquin Castro , D-Texas , said","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"that he plans to introduce a `` resolution","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"to terminate ''","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that could block the emergency declaration .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Such a measure would likely pass in the Democrat-controlled House","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"and could make it through the Senate ,","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"where a number of Republicans have objected to the precedent","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"set by Trump 's use of executive authority .","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"But","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"if the resolution made it through both chambers ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"the president would almost certainly veto it .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"It is unlikely that enough congressional Republicans would join Democrats","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"to override a veto .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"`` Obviously , the president is going to protect his national emergency declaration , ''","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Miller said Sunday","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"when asked","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"if he thought","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Trump would veto such a resolution .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Ann Coulter and Hannity ? :","depth":4},{"id":141,"text":"The off-topic things","depth":5},{"id":142,"text":"Trump said in national emergency speech","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":144,"text":"Emergency declaration is clearest sign","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"Donald Trump and Republicans are divided going into 2020 campaign","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":291,"left":166,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":163,"right":165,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":148,"right":162,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":0,"right":147,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":156,"right":161,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":3,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":4,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":149,"right":153,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":7,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":150,"right":151,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":157,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":159,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":14